  "page": "Baelon Targaryen",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Baelon Targaryen</b> is the name of several members of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>: \n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Baelon_Targaryen_(son_of_Aerys)\" title=\"Baelon Targaryen (son of Aerys)\">Baelon Targaryen</a>, second son of Lord Aerys Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Baelon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Baelon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Baelon Targaryen</a>, third son and fourth child of King Jaehaerys I and Queen Alysanne Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Baelon_Targaryen_(son_of_Viserys_I)\" title=\"Baelon Targaryen (son of Viserys I)\">Baelon Targaryen</a>, second son of King Viserys I Targaryen and Queen Aemma Arryn</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Feminine_equivalent\">Feminine equivalent</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Baelon_Targaryen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Feminine equivalent\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Baela_Targaryen\" title=\"Baela Targaryen\">Baela Targaryen</a>, eldest twin daughter of Prince Daemon Targaryen and Lady Laena Velaryon</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Baelon_Targaryen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Baelor_Targaryen\" title=\"Baelor Targaryen\">Baelor Targaryen</a> (disambiguation)</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403133917\nCache expiry: 1209600\nD